collections.description:
Part of the Black Obsidian collection, this piece embodies the philosophy of dark techno and modern elegance. Guyver is a profound manifestation of the fusion between human essence and mechanical perfection. Inspired by the concept of an androgynous future, this artwork reflects the inner struggle between light and shadow, reason and emotion. The glossy surface of black obsidian symbolizes mystery, strength, and absolute uniqueness.
The Black Obsidian collection challenges stereotypes, offering a deep dive into the world of transhumanism, where the boundaries between the organic and artificial dissolve. Each piece is crafted with an emphasis on intricate detail, powerful soundscapes, and an atmosphere of vastness.

collections.name: The Gods
collections.description:
Chibi Style Collector’s Cards: The Gods Edition

Step into a world where divine power meets adorable artistry! Our Chibi Style Collector’s Cards: The Gods Edition reimagines deities from various mythologies in a uniquely charming and collectible format. Each card features a whimsical, highly stylized chibi depiction of legendary gods and goddesses, capturing their iconic symbols, powers, and personalities in a delightful, pocket-sized form.

Key Features:
	•	Chibi Art Style: Playful, exaggerated proportions with big expressive eyes and vibrant colors.
	•	Holographic & Rare Variants: Special foil cards add a touch of divine radiance.
	•	Pantheon Variety: Explore Greek, Norse, Egyptian, Hindu, and other mythologies.
	•	Power Stats & Lore: Each card includes fun facts and abilities tailored to the deity’s myth.
	•	Limited Editions & Expansions: Collect seasonal, event-exclusive, and legendary god-tier cards.

Perfect for mythology enthusiasts, collectors, & fans of cute, stylized artwork.

collections.name: Butterfly Proyect
collections.description:
Butterfly project is an initiative created by parents and people who have beautiful autistic beings in our lives. We see a lot of light and innocence in them, we love them and we want their future to be bright.

The art that we show through butterflies represents the transformation of autistic people who manage to have therapies and support in their development. We call to raise awareness and notice the great difference that exists between treated autism and those that do not do so due to lack of resources.

RJ- A father with a beautiful AUTISTIC son.

collections.name: ElmonX The Kiss
collections.description: The Kiss by Gustav Klimt is one of the most famous and celebrated paintings in the world, symbolizing love, passion, and artistic brilliance. Created between 1907 and 1908 during Klimt's "Golden Period," the masterpiece features a couple locked in an intimate embrace, enveloped in shimmering gold and intricate patterns. With its mesmerizing mix of Symbolism and Art Nouveau, The Kiss has captivated audiences for over a century and remains a timeless icon of romance and beauty. This is the first opportunity to own 'The Kiss' digital collectible as a premium digital artwork in 3D by ElmonX. Holders can view and interact with the NFT in Augmented Reality.

collections.name: Floral Imagination Studio
collections.description:
Floral Imagination” is a digital art collection that elevates real flowers to a new form.
Floral Imagination takes photographs of flowers and uses a unique stylistic transformation technique to add an artistic essence to the beauty of nature.

Each piece is assigned a unique number, and each piece unfolds a different floral story. The number is not just an identification, but also a key to enjoying the evolution of the series.

We hope you enjoy this beautiful world where the boundaries between the natural and the digital blend together.
